name: SilkChocolateHypnotic
description: Can you outstare the silk chocolate? Born of many explorations and experiments within the seething mass that is the ThoughtWater algorithm. True to its roots as a psychedelic hypnotiser, this simple yet perfect loop will have you and guests gazing into the liquid infinite for far too long! The artist reserves the right to produce derivative works and promotionals. However this remains the first of it's kind!
